      "rationale": "SST k-ω was selected based on published benchmark against LES for rotating confined flows (Pasquetti 2022); NIH difference vs. LES reference < 7%. Giersiepen-Wurzinger model benchmarked against Heuser-Opitz data; within published scatter band. Two additional turbulence models (realizable k-ε, RSM) compared; NIH spread 9.4%, within model form uncertainty budget. Achieves Gradation 4."
