      "rationale": "Geometry inputs derived from CMM measurements (uncertainty ±0.01 mm). Fluid properties from ASTM F1841 and Merrill (1969) with documented uncertainty. Monte Carlo propagation with 1000 LHS samples yielded NIH 95% CI of ±6.2% at the worst-case operating point. All inputs archived in a traceable input deck. Achieves Gradation 5."
